{"tid":1672003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港反共但支持愛共的加泰？","createTime":"2019-10-24T00:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:16.000Z","uid":53735,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ae0db7073a046ddc106b232c16fdef270f6b88","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:21:03.000Z","msg":"儍的嗎？"},{"pid":"b58bf55948399008253694c6b1b99a553e05e2c9","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"反共就是反共<br />\n加泰愛共產黨，有乜理由去支持佢同歐洲美國反面"},{"pid":"84fafdfa98a9e5f9792b819cbb41f431b66009af","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"獨家爆料。中共意圖借出巨款110億歐元支持加泰獨立，建立中央銀行。<br />\n//根據報導，西班牙警方搜查2016年5月17日的郵件，中國曾要求在借出這110億歐元之前，要先知道加泰是要&ldquo;單方面宣布獨立&rdquo;，還是要與&ldquo;西班牙政府談判&rdquo;。根據文件中顯示，一旦加泰宣布獨立，就會立即借出這筆錢。<br />\n報導刊出之後，加泰流亡領袖Puigdemont出了個tweet，＂有什麼問題，他們又不是俄羅斯人＂<br />\nCarles Puigdemont<br />\n@KRLS<br />\nPer&ograve; no hav&iacute;em quedat que eren els russos[???]<br />\n上年有西班牙報章報導，加泰流亡獨派政府，曾經向中國尋求110億歐元貸款，以建立加泰羅尼亞中央銀行。//"},{"pid":"70b14d4dbdeb8875205ecbae9c331eba0a9adf59","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mxdw4Fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxdw4Fk.png&h=83cb60a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elperiodico.com/es/politica/20181027/la-generalitat-busco-fondos-en-china-para-crear-un-banco-central-de-catalunya-7114000?fbclid=IwAR2HiJ7hq-59MoAQfAtlOKoKe5hY5iJgB4db7OaP-CAWI0ivVrp0FdzRZV0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elperiodico.com%2Fes%2Fpolitica%2F20181027%2Fla-generalitat-busco-fondos-en-china-para-crear-un-banco-central-de-catalunya-7114000%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2HiJ7hq-59MoAQfAtlOKoKe5hY5iJgB4db7OaP-CAWI0ivVrp0FdzRZV0&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUod8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=2b875446\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elperiodico.com/es/politica/20181027/la-generalitat-busco-fondos-en-china-para-crear-un-banco-central-de-catalunya-7114000?fbclid=IwAR2HiJ7hq-59MoAQfAtlOKoKe5hY5iJgB4db7OaP-CAWI0ivVrp0FdzRZV0</a>"},{"pid":"a7cd4512526abaeab618dbdcd290f2fa76ec623c","tid":1672003,"uid":180124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"有po踢爆得少數政黨人士係親共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同咪張舉共旗相已經2年前<br />\n咪再用哩點狙擊人啦你聊"},{"pid":"10842e242e4d535226e7c1b37a622ac7403b3d7e","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"收中共錢是朋友還是敵人？"},{"pid":"99953460d8fbdf9d2ded6cb1fe7f411b35aab431","tid":1672003,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"［有位走地撐加泰獨立］ 每個地方既人民應擁有自決自己地方前途的權力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bac54ce386778df300a3e54c69498ef368ec26a8","tid":1672003,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"呢個應該推<br />\n真係唔知加泰受中共支持"},{"pid":"1daedfa0f3e5c17bff04d31eeec99cbd87c6f70d","tid":1672003,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒聲援的加泰獨立運動，有社會主義建國的宗旨，更被西班牙警方證實加泰獨立運動意圖接受中共110億歐元貸款，以建立加泰獨立之後的中央銀行。<br />\n加泰獨立運動在歐洲及美國聲名狼藉，流亡領袖無國家願意收留（被比利時遣返西班牙受審），但在香港卻受到黃之鋒及偽港獨派的高舉，今日要舉行大會來聲援加泰獨立，這是什麼原因呢？<br />\n黃之鋒可不可以今晚現身聲援加泰獨立大會，親自解釋一下呢？<br />\n（圖片來源：網絡）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYeDK2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYeDK2q.jpg&h=2cadb6a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abe452f4c969b66401abb3a894ee1cfa7914f724","tid":1672003,"uid":62321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"反共同反中共好似係兩樣野黎<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔支持撐加泰集會"},{"pid":"d54a8b1432103